CHAPTER 15
EFFECTIVE DATE
These regulations were originally effective on January 2, 1975, amended and
superceding the Zoning Ordinance of the Town of Franklin adopted August
1966. These amended Regulations are effective February 1, 1988. Further
amendments to these Regulations were:
Adopted April 4, 1989 - effective April 7, 1989;
Adopted August 15, 1989 - effective August 19, 1989;
